    <a name="buttons" id="buttons"></a>
    <h2 class="reference-heading">Buttons</h2>
    <p class="reference-text">The following variant classes can be added to <code>.cta</code>: <code>.cta--full</code> for full width, <code>.cta--full-mobile</code> for full width only on mobile, <code>.cta--no-mobile</code> to hide on mobile, <code>.cta--right</code> to float right on tablet and desktop; as well as the below.</p>

    <code class="code-label">.cta</code>
    <input type="button" class="cta" value=".cta default" />

    <code class="code-label">.cta--secondary</code>
    <input type="button" class="cta cta--secondary" value=".cta--secondary" />
